  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t日韩老人，从权贵到平民，穿着正装的证件照，都给人一种整洁、洋气、庄重的感觉，很有高级感<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvODdmMjc5ZTk4YjEyODI4NGU1ZDhkLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/87f279e98b128284e5d8d.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/87f279e98b128284e5d8d.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/87f279e98b128284e5d8d.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvYTk5ZWQ2NzhiMzE4MDA1ZGMwMTgxLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/a99ed678b318005dc0181.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/a99ed678b318005dc0181.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/a99ed678b318005dc0181.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n中国老人，哪怕是民国大学生蛤，也是伴随着一股子土气和韭气。建国前的照片倒还能看看。<br/>\n<br/>\n不仅是老人的气度，就连日韩美国的学生证件照，都比中国的学生证件照好看不少！无论从精神面貌还是穿着品味上！<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNWYzZTZlNjBlZmQ1NDIyNmY4MmIyLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/5f3e6e60efd54226f82b2.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/5f3e6e60efd54226f82b2.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/5f3e6e60efd54226f82b2.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvYmJjZTJmODNjN2M0ZDQ4NTc1NDc1LmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/bbce2f83c7c4d48575475.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/bbce2f83c7c4d48575475.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/bbce2f83c7c4d48575475.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZTMyNzM0NmU5NWQ3MDA3Y2QzMzNiLnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/e327346e95d7007cd333b.png\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/e327346e95d7007cd333b.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/e327346e95d7007cd333b.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n是因为中国的审美彻底被CCP给破坏了吗？我们怎么就拍不出有高级感的照片？\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
